4. **Fix mobile orders table selection**  
Ensure your mobile-orders page imports and uses the `/api/tables/mobile/tables_layout/` endpoint, and that your Next.js rewrites include:
```js
async rewrites() {
  return [
    { source: '/api/tables/mobile/:path*', destination: 'https://hotelrshammad.co.in/api/tables/mobile/:path*' },
    // ...other rewrites
  ];
}



const res = await fetch('/api/tables/mobile/tables_layout/', { headers: { Authorization: `Bearer ${user.access}` } });
